                     <interp inst="t17960406-7-person107" type="gender" value="female"></interp>
                  </persName>
            , spinster, married at this church, by banns, the 24th of January, 1796, by me 
               <persName id="t17960406-7-person108">
                  Griffith
                   Griffiths
